      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DR. AURORA (5) still a maiden after 24 runs but rarely out of the placings. Was in the placings again last time finishing second (25.28) at this track. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from five attempts. Makes plenty of appeal. FLYWHEEL NEIL (8) was in the money two back in a Maiden at this track then jumped from a squeeze draw last time and was not far away when second (24.84) over 435m at this track. Can turn it around this time. DODGING SHADOWS (7) produced a moderate effort last time when fifth at Warragul over 400m behind Paw Melody (23.71) in a Maiden. Likely to play a prominent role. PAW XELA (2) is worth consideration after filling a hole last start.",
